WEBVTT

01:26.640 --> 01:28.760
-What have you got?
-Parathas.

01:29.640 --> 01:31.360
-Where's the pickle?
-I didn't bring it.

01:31.920 --> 01:33.480
-Why?
-I forgot.

01:33.560 --> 01:35.360
You want me to eat it with plain air?

01:35.440 --> 01:37.000
If you want to.

01:37.920 --> 01:39.400
-Idiot.
-You're an idiot!

01:40.280 --> 01:42.560
-Fool!
-You're a fool!

01:42.640 --> 01:45.200
Eat it if you want,
or dump it in the canal.

01:47.400 --> 01:49.560
You're going to get whacked today.

01:49.760 --> 01:52.080
You'll be walking around with a red butt.

01:52.760 --> 01:55.000
Sattu was looking for you.

01:55.200 --> 01:56.600
He was angry.

01:56.760 --> 01:59.800
He was fuming with anger.

01:59.880 --> 02:03.760
He wants to send you to a
boarding school in London.

02:03.920 --> 02:05.440
As if mom will let him.

02:05.520 --> 02:06.680
"Send me to London!"

02:06.760 --> 02:08.120
Idiotic Sattu.

02:10.600 --> 02:12.240
Why are you staring at me?

02:12.520 --> 02:13.840
Go, get me some water.

02:14.000 --> 02:15.320
Get it yourself.

02:15.440 --> 02:16.840
Get it or else...

02:16.920 --> 02:19.560
-What will you do?
-I'll bite you.

02:19.640 --> 02:21.040
I'll scratch you.

02:36.800 --> 02:39.560
I swear, Sattu. I didn't smoke.

02:41.880 --> 02:43.200
Why are you hitting me?

02:43.400 --> 02:45.200
You don't call your father by his name.

02:46.360 --> 02:49.760
-But grandma calls you Sattu.
-She's my mother.

02:49.920 --> 02:53.680
-But even my mother calls you Sattu.
-Sattu!

02:55.040 --> 02:56.640
Why are you hitting me?

02:57.280 --> 02:58.760
Don't look at me.

03:00.040 --> 03:02.320
Was your teacher lying
when he told me you smoked?

03:02.640 --> 03:05.720
Make up your mind about
why you're hitting me.

03:05.800 --> 03:10.160
For smoking or for calling you Sattu?

03:10.800 --> 03:12.080
Shut up.

03:13.960 --> 03:16.720
He's going abroad, Kaushalya.
And that's final.

03:18.080 --> 03:19.800
He'll die without us.

03:20.080 --> 03:22.360
And if he stays here,
he'll bring us shame.

03:22.440 --> 03:25.240
He's so unmannered.
Calls his dad by his name.

03:25.520 --> 03:26.600
What should I call you?

03:26.680 --> 03:29.240
When I call you "dad"
Kaushalya glares at me.

03:29.360 --> 03:30.920
-Oh, God!
-Shut up.

03:33.240 --> 03:35.440
Pack his bags,
he's leaving tomorrow.

03:36.160 --> 03:37.200
Tomorrow?

03:37.280 --> 03:39.080
Be grateful that I've given
you both one night

03:39.160 --> 03:40.640
to do all your emotional
"give and takes."

03:44.120 --> 03:45.920
-Sattu's gone mad.
-Shut up.

03:46.000 --> 03:49.200
-Sattu!
-Shameless boy!

04:08.760 --> 04:10.640
I'm growing bigger day-by-day.

04:12.200 --> 04:13.480
How big?

04:14.360 --> 04:15.880
Big enough for you.

04:16.600 --> 04:19.560
Mom said I should get married

04:19.640 --> 04:24.600
or someone else will take me away.

04:25.160 --> 04:28.080
Tell her no.

04:28.200 --> 04:33.560
I was going to tell her that I won't
let anybody touch me except Dev.

04:37.960 --> 04:41.320
Paro, I am going insane.

04:45.200 --> 04:46.720
I'm also losing it.

04:48.480 --> 04:49.640
Come back soon.

04:50.400 --> 04:51.960
You're losing it? I've lost it.

04:52.600 --> 04:53.760
Yes, I've lost it too.

04:54.200 --> 04:55.720
You just said you were losing it.

04:55.960 --> 05:00.480
Yes, I was, now I have totally lost it.

05:05.960 --> 05:07.040
Paro.

05:22.000 --> 05:23.080
Tell me.

05:30.880 --> 05:31.800
Paro.

05:34.960 --> 05:37.640
-Send me your photograph.
-You already have one.

05:39.800 --> 05:41.240
A naked one.

05:43.440 --> 05:44.560
Have you gone crazy?

06:23.120 --> 06:26.080
If you ever tell me to do
such a crazy thing again, I'll kill you.

06:26.320 --> 06:29.920
Do you even know how difficult it was?

06:30.760 --> 06:34.080
My heart was pounding like an engine.

06:35.120 --> 06:37.320
I felt like everyone was staring at me.

06:37.400 --> 06:39.160
And that photo shop owner
was staring at me

06:39.240 --> 06:40.560
as if he had never seen them before.

06:40.880 --> 06:44.240
As if his wife applies pimple-removers!
Bloody dog!

06:44.640 --> 06:46.520
Tell me how to use the scanner.
I'll do it myself.

06:46.600 --> 06:48.600
Ma'am, why are you taking
the trouble when I am here?

06:48.720 --> 06:51.640
I'll do such a brilliant job,
it will bring life to the photo.

06:51.720 --> 06:53.520
Don't you get it, fatso?

07:11.880 --> 07:15.000
Paro, I'm coming back.

07:49.160 --> 07:52.400
Eat it. Come on.

08:43.760 --> 08:45.040
Throw it away.

09:07.960 --> 09:09.320
It's Dwij's Haldi Ceremony today.

10:16.280 --> 10:19.560
Paro, you're going to get married next.

10:22.400 --> 10:23.760
Hey, Paro!

11:42.480 --> 11:43.480
What happened?

11:49.160 --> 11:51.760
Dev, how are you?

11:51.920 --> 11:52.920
Manager Uncle.

11:53.000 --> 11:54.240
I am absolutely fine.

11:54.440 --> 11:56.520
Haven't seen you in ages.

11:57.640 --> 12:00.480
Son, what's on your shirt?

12:01.080 --> 12:02.160
I don't know.

12:03.240 --> 12:05.000
It looks like Haldi.

12:08.440 --> 12:10.200
It even smells like Haldi.

12:13.600 --> 12:15.760
-It is Haldi.
-Yes.

12:24.040 --> 12:25.400
Paro?

12:27.000 --> 12:29.080
What are you
searching for on the floor?

12:30.720 --> 12:33.200
Well... my earrings.

12:33.600 --> 12:36.960
-Then what's on your ears?
-On my ears?

12:38.720 --> 12:41.240
Well, earrings.

12:41.440 --> 12:45.280
-Paro, come out.
-Yes.

12:46.840 --> 12:48.520
What's on your hands?

12:50.760 --> 12:52.360
It looks like Haldi.

12:55.600 --> 12:57.320
It even smells like Haldi.

13:00.600 --> 13:02.520
It is Haldi.

13:04.600 --> 13:06.520
Paro, go out.

13:38.520 --> 13:41.040
Welcome, sir. I'm Sunil.

13:41.240 --> 13:42.400
Come along.

13:44.760 --> 13:45.920
This way.

13:47.840 --> 13:50.760
Sir, the sugarcane juice
crystallizes and gets collected here.

13:50.840 --> 13:53.520
And this is where we check
if it has turned into sugar.

13:54.840 --> 13:56.280
Hello, son.

14:22.760 --> 14:24.280
First time?

14:24.960 --> 14:27.400
No?

14:39.800 --> 14:42.080
-You can't put your hands in.
-Why not?

14:42.160 --> 14:43.480
My dress is too tight.

14:43.920 --> 14:47.320
-Can I rip it?
-So that I roam around naked?

14:48.120 --> 14:50.480
-Let go of my hands.
-I won't.

14:50.640 --> 14:54.200
-I am a Punjabi girl.
-I am also a Punjabi boy.

15:05.640 --> 15:06.680
Paro!

15:06.760 --> 15:08.360
-Paro!
-Yes. I'm coming.

15:09.520 --> 15:11.760
-Paro.
-Coming!

15:12.120 --> 15:14.200
-What are you doing there?
-Don't come here.

15:14.280 --> 15:15.560
I'll be right there.

15:15.960 --> 15:18.160
Your father will surely die one day.

15:24.240 --> 15:25.120
What were you doing there?

15:25.200 --> 15:26.880
There's a long queue
outside the toilet.

15:27.120 --> 15:28.320
What?

15:40.040 --> 15:42.520
What if the dogs come inside?

15:46.200 --> 15:49.120
Paro. Paro!

15:50.560 --> 15:51.680
Open the...

15:54.880 --> 15:57.160
There's a long queue
outside the toilet.

16:05.600 --> 16:07.280
-Hey, you.
-Paro.

16:09.000 --> 16:10.160
Do something.

16:10.360 --> 16:13.160
-What do I do?
-Find a solution.

16:14.160 --> 16:15.680
So desperate?

16:16.560 --> 16:17.480
Yes.

16:18.480 --> 16:19.560
That's good.

16:20.520 --> 16:21.680
Paro...

16:29.160 --> 16:30.600
Dev.

16:31.280 --> 16:33.800
I know that you've studied in London.

16:34.040 --> 16:35.480
Even I'm going there.

16:35.560 --> 16:36.880
-Oxford.
-Are you?

16:43.120 --> 16:47.120
Aunt Kaushalya wants us
to get something from the farm.

16:48.000 --> 16:51.360
-Is it?
-Shall we?

16:52.840 --> 16:54.040
Come on.

17:20.760 --> 17:22.599
-Listen.
-What?

17:23.040 --> 17:24.680
-I'll be back.
-Okay.

17:34.360 --> 17:35.720
Tell me.

17:40.240 --> 17:41.800
I need the keys to your room.

17:41.880 --> 17:44.000
-Why?
-My Dev is back.

17:44.600 --> 17:45.920
So, why should I give you the keys?

17:46.400 --> 17:47.320
Come on.

17:47.600 --> 17:49.120
I love you.

17:49.480 --> 17:52.720
If you want Dev,
why don't you do it in his room?

17:55.720 --> 17:57.880
Don't you get it?
There are so many people around.

17:57.960 --> 17:59.160
There's a wedding going on.

17:59.600 --> 18:01.360
Have I ever said no to you?

18:01.440 --> 18:02.960
I love you.

18:03.320 --> 18:05.520
First look at yourself! "Loves me."

18:05.720 --> 18:08.320
Be grateful that...
Get lost!

18:08.800 --> 18:10.760
Aunt, you've given the
servants a free hand here.

18:10.840 --> 18:12.360
-Look at him.
-What happened?

18:35.840 --> 18:37.200
What happened?

18:49.680 --> 18:50.840
Look.

19:18.480 --> 19:23.080
Paro is the most
sensuous girl in this village.

19:23.360 --> 19:24.360
You're right.

19:24.440 --> 19:26.080
She can break the bed.

19:27.080 --> 19:28.960
She can bake you to death, man.

19:30.240 --> 19:31.880
Murder you in bed!

19:32.160 --> 19:34.000
-Greetings, sir.
-Sir.

19:49.200 --> 19:51.480
-Where were you?
-I had gone for an outing.

19:51.560 --> 19:53.040
-Alone?
-Yes.

19:53.760 --> 19:55.920
-Brother!
-There she is.

19:57.040 --> 20:00.600
-Dad, when did you arrive?
-Just now.

20:00.680 --> 20:02.520
-How are you?
-I'm fine.

20:02.600 --> 20:04.320
-Are you all right?
-Absolutely.

20:14.440 --> 20:17.360
I swear on my dead mother.
She's insatiable.

20:17.440 --> 20:18.760
I was so worn out and sore.

20:19.120 --> 20:22.280
I couldn't get up for two days.
I was hurting.

20:23.160 --> 20:27.080
I am telling you, Sir.
No one can beat Paro.

20:27.440 --> 20:28.360
You're lying.

20:28.440 --> 20:30.880
Curse my dead mother's soul if I'm lying.

20:30.960 --> 20:33.240
She wanted to do
it a while back.

20:33.320 --> 20:34.800
I was so scared I said no.

20:36.040 --> 20:40.040
Why are you glaring
at me like that, sir?

20:40.120 --> 20:43.360
All you have to do is ask
and she'll ride you to eternity.

20:44.800 --> 20:46.440
But I'm very surprised, sir.

20:46.760 --> 20:50.120
You haven't done it
with her yet? I'm shocked.

21:01.400 --> 21:03.840
Hey! What did you do?

21:10.600 --> 21:11.600
What happened?

21:12.880 --> 21:15.320
-Please go out.
-But what happened?

21:16.280 --> 21:17.880
Leave me alone, please.

21:21.680 --> 21:23.560
-What happened?
-Nothing.

21:24.240 --> 21:25.680
London has ruined him.

21:25.960 --> 21:27.480
At least find out what happened.

21:27.560 --> 21:29.120
Let's go out. I'll tell you.

23:14.720 --> 23:15.880
What are you doing?

23:16.960 --> 23:20.200
You asked me to do something.
So, here I am.

23:21.080 --> 23:22.200
Put your hands up.

23:33.640 --> 23:35.200
You're so hairy.

23:40.200 --> 23:41.600
You're such an expert.

23:42.760 --> 23:44.320
How many have you done it with?

23:52.880 --> 23:54.280
Get your hands off!

23:59.880 --> 24:01.200
I said take your hands off!

24:05.240 --> 24:07.200
-Where are you going?
-Let me go.

24:08.400 --> 24:09.800
Tell me what happened.

24:10.160 --> 24:11.400
I said let me go.

24:11.600 --> 24:12.800
You!

24:57.640 --> 24:59.400
There you are.
And why are you carrying that?

24:59.480 --> 25:01.080
Aunt had asked for it.

25:01.160 --> 25:03.080
She was falling
short of mattresses.

25:04.520 --> 25:08.120
Come, dear. Your dad wants to
talk to you. Let's go inside.

25:14.360 --> 25:15.800
Yes, tell me.

25:17.480 --> 25:20.200
-Sit.
-No. Tell me.

25:22.520 --> 25:27.040
Have you met Bhuvan Singh...

25:27.400 --> 25:28.760
who's here for the wedding?

25:28.960 --> 25:30.360
Bhuvan Singh who?

25:30.680 --> 25:33.360
That girl, Rasika's brother.

25:33.920 --> 25:37.800
He likes you.
He wants to marry you.

25:38.240 --> 25:39.800
So what if he likes me?

25:41.360 --> 25:43.440
They're very well-off.

25:43.520 --> 25:45.000
I will only marry Dev.

25:45.080 --> 25:46.960
And will wait for him
till he marries me.

25:47.040 --> 25:48.280
Have you gone crazy?

25:48.560 --> 25:51.440
Why would Satpal
marry his son to you?

25:51.520 --> 25:54.600
Why wouldn't he?
I've made lassi for him all my life.

25:54.680 --> 25:56.280
He loves me so much.

25:56.640 --> 25:59.760
That's okay. But he's my boss.
We're out of his league.

25:59.840 --> 26:04.040
Dev studied in London,
you studied here.

26:04.120 --> 26:07.320
I aced my exams and Dev
barely scraped through his.

26:07.560 --> 26:09.320
At least, try talking to him.

26:09.400 --> 26:10.600
I don't want to embarrass myself.

26:10.680 --> 26:13.720
But you can embarrass
your daughter, right?

26:16.240 --> 26:17.640
Please meet Bhuvan.

26:17.720 --> 26:20.360
Bring him close to me and
I'll chop him into pieces.

26:20.880 --> 26:22.560
Paro!

26:23.200 --> 26:25.040
Paro! Paro!

26:25.120 --> 26:26.480
Listen to me, dear.

26:26.560 --> 26:28.240
Where are you going?

26:32.080 --> 26:33.800
Move aside. Let go.

26:39.000 --> 26:41.080
-Paro.
-Father has gone insane!

26:41.160 --> 26:42.320
He needs treatment.

26:42.400 --> 26:46.480
He's right. Why should
Satpal marry his son to you?

26:46.960 --> 26:50.640
Even Dev has grown up.
Who knows where his heart is.

26:50.720 --> 26:54.080
I know where it is.
He gave it to me when we were kids.

26:55.360 --> 26:59.400
-The bucket is overflowing, my dear.
-I know!

27:02.680 --> 27:05.400
Paro, where are you going?

27:08.680 --> 27:11.840
What kind of a chef is he?
Look what he has done to the rotis.

27:11.920 --> 27:14.040
He has burnt them.

27:14.120 --> 27:17.120
Do your job.
Don't interfere in his.

27:17.200 --> 27:19.520
-Is everything all right?
-Yes.

27:22.680 --> 27:26.960
Finish up, quickly.
We've to sing and dance too. Keep it here.

27:27.040 --> 27:29.440
Paro, come here.

27:30.080 --> 27:31.960
Take this cup of tea to your uncle.

27:32.040 --> 27:33.720
I don't know what is
wrong with this girl.

27:33.800 --> 27:35.360
It's very tasty.

27:35.440 --> 27:38.080
-Please, take it.
-No, that's enough.

27:38.320 --> 27:40.080
Paro, come join us.

27:40.160 --> 27:42.880
-Later.
-Where are you going?

28:03.200 --> 28:04.680
You are Bhuvan's sister, right?

28:04.760 --> 28:06.600
Please don't tell anything to my brother.

28:06.680 --> 28:08.000
Get out.

28:13.080 --> 28:14.480
What were you doing with her?

28:15.320 --> 28:17.240
The same that you do with Sunil.

28:17.520 --> 28:18.800
With Sunil?

28:19.200 --> 28:20.960
What did I do with Sunil?

28:28.080 --> 28:29.320
Tell me.

28:30.720 --> 28:32.560
Is that why you broke his head?

28:33.040 --> 28:36.200
-Go away.
-I didn't do anything with that lousy man.

28:36.400 --> 28:37.840
I know everything.

28:38.760 --> 28:40.360
Sunil told you?

28:46.640 --> 28:48.160
When did he tell you?

28:49.440 --> 28:50.520
Exactly before I broke
the bottle on him.

28:50.600 --> 28:52.760
Leave or else
I'll do the same to you.

28:58.240 --> 28:59.320
You hypocrite!

28:59.720 --> 29:02.200
You broke the bottle on him
after taking Rasika out.

29:02.400 --> 29:04.760
What you do is right.
And if I do it...

29:08.320 --> 29:09.520
I'm leaving.

29:11.080 --> 29:13.520
I came to tell you that
I have received a marriage proposal.

29:17.720 --> 29:18.880
Good.

29:19.440 --> 29:21.120
Go ruin someone else's life.

29:21.560 --> 29:23.760
Anyway, you're not good
enough to get married to me.

29:25.560 --> 29:27.760
A servant's daughter
remains just that, a servant.

29:29.080 --> 29:30.280
Look at yourself.

29:30.960 --> 29:34.960
Unkempt hair,
lousy clothes, ugly as hell.

29:36.760 --> 29:38.000
Illiterate!

