-Stop!

31:36.760 --> 31:38.720
-Run, Sunil!
-Stop. I won't spare you.

31:38.800 --> 31:43.880
Why are you running away?
Stop!

31:44.200 --> 31:45.880
She has gone crazy!

31:48.000 --> 31:49.160
Paro!

31:49.560 --> 31:51.960
Paro, what are you doing?
Have you lost your mind?

31:52.280 --> 31:53.480
Hey, Paro!

31:53.880 --> 31:57.760
-Give the matchbox.
-You'll tear my shirt. Let go.

31:57.840 --> 31:58.840
Give the matchbox!

31:58.920 --> 32:01.400
That's the only other shirt I have!

32:01.480 --> 32:04.600
Paro, please don't burn it.

32:04.720 --> 32:07.480
He burnt my dreams,
I'll burn down his house!

32:07.560 --> 32:08.800
